node.text: DIOS, oramos por que nuestros hermanos Cubanos al fin tenga libertad y paz en su pueblo. Te pedimos por la salud y el bien estar de todos aquello en la isla que están sufriendo. Señor todo poderoso te pedimos que manifiestes cambio! Que ilumines a todos los que están en poder a ser decisiones que unifiquen el país y su comunidad. Libertad para Cuba…En el nombre del Padre, del Hijo y del Espíritu Santo. #fé #soscuba 🇨🇺 #TeamLeJuan
That one friend who’s always talking about their Diet. 😂 #TeamLeJuan

node.text: One of the most important things my father taught me was to listen and respect the woman I love. He never once told me this, but he never needed to because he always set the example at home. A true gentleman and my role model. Happy Father Day Pa! 🖤 @LeDadJames #TeamLeJuan

node.text: 4 years ago God blessed me by allowing me to achieve a long life dream of buying my parents the home they always deserved. Since that emotional day, I’ve dreamt of the moment @camilaainc and I would be able to buy a home of our own. Today I’m happy announce that thanks to God, our families, and of course you all, we have made those dreams a reality 🏠🤩🔑 #Orlando #Florida #TeamLeJuan

node.text:
The time has come for the next chapter in our lives. Today we are moving out of our condo. This was my first big investment 6 years ago. So many memories in this place. My all time favorite was asking Cam to marry me in this exact same spot. Definitely a bittersweet feeling, but we are not selling this place so maybe one day we’ll retire here together. For now, it’s time for our next journey! 📦🚛

Can you guess where we are moving to next.. are we leaving or staying in Orlando? Are we leaving Florida? If so, where ? Drop your prediction down below 👇🏼 #TeamLeJuan
All Hispanic Women have that one “EX” 😂❌ #tbt #TeamLeJuan
